Abstract = {{The productivity of passion fruit in Maranhao State, Brazil, is very
   low, because the deficient utilization of technologies by the
   smallholders. The present study was carried out to evaluate the effect
   of pollination on the fruiting set and fruit quality, and the frequency
   of visiting on flowers of carpenter bees (Xylocopa spp.) on passion
   fruit species Passiflora edulis Sims f. flavicarpa Deg. And Passiflora
