   species of Goniocolletes (Goinocolletes anthedonus sp.n.; Goniocolletes
   badius sp.n.; Goniocolletes ciliatus sp.n.; Goniocolletes comatus sp.n.;
   Goniocolletes dasypus sp.n.; Goniocolletes parvus sp.n.; Goniocolletes
   rugosus sp.n.) and 13 new species of Leioproctus (Leioproctus
   (Minycolletes) aquilus sp.n.; Leioproctus (Leioproctus) crinitus sp.n.;
