   Leioproctus (Minycolletes) paulus sp.n.; Leioproctus (Minycolletes)
   pygmaeus sp.n.; Leioproctus (Leioproctus) quadrimaculatus sp.n.;
   Leioproctus (Fragocolletes) rutiliventris sp.n.; Leioproctus
   (Charicolletes) saltus sp.n., and Leioproctus (Alokocolletes) sequax
   sp.n.) are described. Additionally seven new species-level synonymies
